{
  "stem": "13471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went, first of all, to Geneva because Geneva had been the United Nations-- the League of Nations.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got a few from there, but very few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finally-- I found that the best source was Holland because if you're-- if you're live in one of the small European countries-- let's suppose you want to become a engineer and you're a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go through the university up to a certain level, but then when are-- where are you going to get a series of texts on strain gauges with high tensile steel in Dutch?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't exist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to know French, German, English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And their, their upper education has to include texts and materials and so forth in French, German, English.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Geneva, I went to the United-- to the League of Nations office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still sort of a half-dead organization at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Holland, there had been a special interpreters or translators core in the Dutch army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had been disbanded, but I found the former commanding officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he put-- he had some names and lists, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I found a very fine place was the Paris telephone exchange because [LAUGHS] you-- in Paris, who's at these various upper class hotels?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're Frenchmen, they're Britishers, they're Spanish, they're-- they're Russians, they're Italians and Swedes, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of these women have to be able to deal with these requests and so put these calls through, [? and so. ?] And so I-- I got quite a few people from the Paris telephone exchange.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I-- did I-- did you hear me telling about, about Virginia Grey at the meeting [? the other night? ?]",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
